spec_data.Name: php-lukasreschke-id3parser
spec_data.Description:
This is a pure ID3 parser based upon getID3.
It supports the following ID3 versions inside MP3 files:

* ID3v1 (v1.0 & v1.1)
* ID3v2 (v2.2, v2.3 & v2.4)

Autoloader: /usr/share/php/ID3Parser/autoload.php
